@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home - HIS</PageTitle>

<h1>Hospital Information System</h1>

<p class="lead">Welcome to the Hospital Information System built with Clean Architecture and Blazor.</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <span class="bi bi-people-fill text-primary"></span> Patient Management
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Manage patient records, including personal information, medical record numbers, and contact details.
                </p>
                <a href="/patients" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Patients</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <span class="bi bi-calendar-check-fill text-success"></span> Appointment Scheduling
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Schedule and manage patient appointments with doctors, track appointment status, and view upcoming schedules.
                </p>
                <a href="/appointments" class="btn btn-success">Go to Appointments</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h3>Architecture Overview</h3>
        <p>This application is built using Clean Architecture principles with the following layers:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Domain Layer:</strong> Contains core business entities and interfaces</li>
            <li><strong>Application Layer:</strong> Implements business logic and use cases</li>
            <li><strong>Infrastructure Layer:</strong> Handles data persistence and external services</li>
            <li><strong>Presentation Layer (Blazor):</strong> Provides the user interface</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

